---
title: Sweet Soy-Glazed Tofu & Sushi Rice with Cucumber Salad & Japanese Dressing
description: Rice bowls are a favourite for something quick, fresh and delicious! Add flavourful marinated tofu, a crunchy slaw and fragrant coriander to a bowl of zingy-sweet sushi rice for a taste explosion.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y25_R1031_W22_NZ_Main_1_high-0cfabc2a.jpg
